|  9 |    4 |    1 | kk      |                               9 |                                               1 |
|  7 |    4 |    2 | 6fe     |                               7 |                                               2 |
| 10 |    4 |    3 | kk      |                              10 |                                               3 |
+----+------+------+---------+---------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------+
